#DAY 5 - RESPONSIVE DESIGN

Technologies Used:
* HTML5
* CSS3
* Flexbox
* Media Queries

Learning Outcome:
This assignment has taught me how modern websites are responsive to various devices.
I am now able to design flexible, usable, and mobile-friendly layouts.

Result:
The webpage is successfully responsive to:
*  Desktop Screens
*  Mobile Devices
*  Tablets

The webpage layout automatically adjusts and reorganizes its content according to the screen size.
